reviewText: Classic Sandro movies. Bought this for my father and he loved it.
VERY GOOD DVD'S ESPECIALLY FOR AGE OF HOW OLD THESE MOVIES REALLY ARE! AS USUAL, SANDRO ROCKS! SINCE HE IDOLIZED ELVIS, YOU CAN SEE HOW MUCH OF AN INFLUNECE THE KING HAD ON HIM! MUST BUY!
The quality of the video is good, the sound is great, but the memories are priceless! I never imagine seeing Sandro in the comfort of my house, thank you!
I love all of the videos & Cd's I got they all sound good and I can see them good too. I know that this movies where done more than 40 yrs ago they look ok!!!
i ordered sandro videos and they came all scrached..therefore i am not a satisfied customer at this time..thank you
